						p What are the <strong>job titles</strong> that convert and engage best?
						p What <strong>geographies</strong> to focus in?
						p What <strong>features</strong> do your best customers value most?
				.col-sm-3

			.row.p-b-lg
				a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href='https://app.madkudu.com/signup') Get a <strong>free customer analysis</strong> in less than 5 minutes
